Email 聯絡 (zysk@ymail.com)&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='replies' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.jamelchui.com/feeds/8185755675946639515/comments/default' title='張貼留言'/><link rel='replies' type='text/html' href='http://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=6814419997133257228&amp;postID=8185755675946639515' title='0 個意見'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/6814419997133257228/posts/default/8185755675946639515'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/6814419997133257228/posts/default/8185755675946639515'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://www.jamelchui.com/2014/01/blog-post_19.html' title='灑家 - 豬油煲仔飯'/><author><name>Jamel Chui</name><uri>https://plus.google.com/100391570887297987812</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='32' height='32' src='//lh6.googleusercontent.com/-vYuwC0-1G9Y/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAFU/M9S6yORa7W8/s512-c/photo.jpg'/></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qg2dFF0b7hU/UtgQERuF8TI/AAAAAAAAN58/RcvWcCGfaGc/s72-c/IMG_2463.jpg" height="72" width="72"/><thr:total>0</thr:total><gd:extendedProperty name="commentSource" value="1"/><gd:extendedProperty name="commentModerationMode" value="FILTERED_POSTMOD"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-6814419997133257228.post-434279303474805735</id><published>2013-08-08T17:00:00.003+08:00</published><updated>2014-01-22T13:21:19.426+08:00</updated><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="九龍 - 觀塘"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="苗。博客活動/試食"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="苗。味の推介"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="苗。玩樂"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="食品 - 雜項"/><title type='text'>Ocean Three Wine - 新品生蠔「白泡泡」及「海公主」</title><content type='html'>&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;早前，參加了&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;OCEAN THEE &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;所舉辦的新品生蠔&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;Workshop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;，了解了生蠔的生長過程、氣候及海水的影響，生蠔的味道亦會有所不同。今次的地點是在OCEAN THREE WINE內舉行，這兒可供客人一邊享用生蠔美食，一邊把酒談歡，除了生蠔及美酒外，還有不少貨品，如調味料、即食鵝肝、急凍產品及海鮮湯等等，十分方便。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/bx_JgKv9GKCbxtuaancIdQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324925&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08068&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a name=&#39;more&#39;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/1XsRePxHyFmWHYoUMAkugg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324924&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08067&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/ozrDOpJDEU8j3Wm5Fq6BGw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324941&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08098&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/IJ3v6qpsWEWWJuE1NonFLw.jpg&quot; id=&quot;1324942&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08101&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;首先由生蠔專家開始講解，生蠔會排出卵子，慢慢變成指甲般大小，成熟後以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;Bags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;amp; Tables&lt;/span&gt;方式分類飼養至適合大小，再清洗乾淨出售。其中有些蠔種會於一個地方養殖，成長至一定大小後，再移至另一個地方養殖，目的令蠔肉吸入不同地方的養份，令味道變得更好，複雜及具層次。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/Y9sbbmuIN39k9VYVK.Zafw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1324926&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08069&quot; width=&quot;265&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/ekTt19A0S3KPlTRDENZyuw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324927&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08073&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;今次品嚐了兩款生蠔，分別是&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;White Foam Oyster&lt;/span&gt;及&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Sea Princess&lt;/span&gt;。前者先於愛爾蘭西北部的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Donegal Bay&lt;/span&gt;生長，因有很多雪山環繞著大海，當雪水溶化後，流入大海，帶進大量礦物質，令浮游生物得到很多養份，生蠔吸入後，令蠔身變得雪白。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/cGHBLQOD4VMJYg82aDEwiQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324928&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08078&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/AoRdn0E1yuI5v1Gc.zl7og.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1324930&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08081&quot; width=&quot;265&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;大約養至三年後，被移送到法國西部的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Marennes-Oleron&lt;/span&gt;進行&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Finishing Tasting&lt;/span&gt;及淨化最少&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;個月，因生蠔每日海水吞吐量達到&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1.5&lt;/span&gt;公升，所以當它吸入兩地海水後，令味道更為獨特。吃落都幾&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Creamy&lt;/span&gt;，味道很鮮甜，配上&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Sartarelli, Vino Spumante, Brut&lt;/span&gt;清爽輕盈的氣泡，更加鮮甜。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/5__4s8cuqBdsLr5vke1u2A.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324929&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08080&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/DFfygz1LusWSjqB1PbdTJQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1324935&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08092&quot; width=&quot;265&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;另一款是&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;Sea Princess&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;，這款生蠔背後有一個淒美的傳說，從前法國有位公主與一位將軍訂下了婚約，但碰巧發生了戰爭，將軍為了保家衛國而戰死沙場，由於將軍都與公主約定在&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;Isigny sur mer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;海灣相見，公主得悉惡耗後，為情自殺，蠔場主人為了紀念這個傳說而將此處出產的生蠔命名為&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;Sea Princess&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;。這款生蠔蠔味較強烈，非常突出，富有礦物味道，較為複雜，配以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;Kaltern,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Muller Thurgau, 2012&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/k1rPdKXpmuSwY1mM8.QrTQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324933&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08089&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/XiPLOGPKGYsKhSZErv2ToQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1324931&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08083&quot; width=&quot;265&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/yT27oytIBTCkPyPgj2QNzg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324934&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08090&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/ecMijInQcZMLWUGRPjSd3A.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1324936&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08093&quot; width=&quot;265&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;還有一系列法式甜點，味道真的不錯，我很喜歡那款&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Opera&lt;/span&gt;，朱古力味濃郁，滲出陣陣酒香，美味，再配上&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Ramandolo&lt;/span&gt;甜酒，可以的選擇。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/qVqsNfaEEfnHsYoriRXNjA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324938&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08095&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/Bi1zu2BlmFYaN_uEwVxu4w.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324939&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08096&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/xfDriRC28b5jc9iKl49DEA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324940&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08097&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/0oIXNyfa1bLZ0UlqBkmmeA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;265&quot; id=&quot;1324932&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08087&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/7oJZna0MMm19P6gDGFAQcw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1324937&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC08094&quot; width=&quot;265&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;整體上，新品生蠔無論在口感或味道上都將突出，尤以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf;&quot;&gt;White Foam&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;Oyster&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6000bf; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;深得大家喜愛。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #38761d; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;Oceanthree Wine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #38761d; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;觀塘開源道60號駱駝漆大廈第三期5樓G座&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; id=&quot;yui-gen21&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 16.363636016845703px; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #fdfefa; color: #333333; font-family: &#39;Droid Serif&#39;; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 新細明體;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #351c75;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot; /&gt;****************************************************&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #fdfefa; color: #333333; font-family: &#39;Droid Serif&#39;; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 新細明體;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #351c75;&quot;&gt;更多有趣的分享，請到&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #fdfefa; color: #333333; font-family: &#39;Droid Serif&#39;; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 新細明體;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #351c75;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Facebook Page (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.facebook.com/jamel.food&quot; style=&quot;color: #7d4417; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;http://www.facebook.com/jamel.food&lt;/a&gt;) &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #fdfefa; color: #333333; font-family: &#39;Droid Serif&#39;; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 新細明體;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #351c75;&quot;&gt;instagram尋找 (jamel_zysk) &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #fdfefa; color: #333333; font-family: &#39;Droid Serif&#39;; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #351c75;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #fdfefa; color: #333333; font-family: &#39;Droid Serif&#39;; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #351c75;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 新細明體;&quot;&gt;Email 聯絡 (zysk@ymail.com)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: xx-small;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot; id=&quot;yui-gen15&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 16.363636016845703px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span st