t;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;上星期日過了一個愉快的下午，既可享受到一頓美味的午餐外，更學曉如何烹調美食。當日受到食友的邀請，來到由&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Eleven&lt;/span&gt;舉辦的「日韓美食祭」&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Tasting Brunch&lt;/span&gt;，他們邀得有「松露女王」之稱的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Esther Au&lt;/span&gt;來教授，並來到她所創辦的「&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Donna Dolce Kitchen Studio&lt;/span&gt;」。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/KnuNHCVUBv9QPipal7qYNA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290676&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04363&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a name=&#39;more&#39;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/NtOlvOjRRR7Ieor5zX04Tg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;89&quot; id=&quot;1290683&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04381&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;separator&quot; style=&quot;clear: both; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/p