&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/iuMBoNF8ixYyyocYdzUaJg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290703&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04468&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;今日的主角是「溫泉玉子」，&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Eleven&lt;/span&gt;特地以&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;65&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;68&lt;/span&gt;度的水慢煮&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;40&lt;/span&gt;分鐘，再進行巴斯德技術殺菌，並擦上食物礦物油來防菌。於是&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Esther&lt;/span&gt;便以此來教授了兩款美食，先是簡單易做的「溫泉玉子伴黑松露荷蘭汁天然酵母包」，接著便是另一款主食「溫泉玉子&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Carbonara&lt;/span&gt;」。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/Hn4tf901uL8aYvfL5JeRiw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290684&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04384&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/F2VxDUfMdfQKEqQ3Xo4IIA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290687&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04393&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/6aslarvH1G0M_kQkLysGtw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290685&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04387&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;「溫泉玉子伴黑松露荷蘭汁天然酵母包」的材料簡單易買，只需要溫泉玉子、巴馬火腿、小露荀及芝士味天然酵母包便可以。說起酵母包，它是我的早餐之選，可是最近沒有了楓糖味，令我有丁點兒失落，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;幸好 其他味道也是不俗的，還有芝士、朱古力、北海道牛奶及南瓜味等選擇。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/zu7SEL7skzdvn2fTEsMyEQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290686&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04389&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/x1d8JzbL1SWrEYXyrg25pA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290691&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.22;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04426&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/BOlFbmqo2iI8sNdEwEGzCw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290677&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04364&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/9f4Px.5o912xgtxBbnXCvQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290679&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04367&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;先是酵母包切半，塗上牛油慢烘煎成微脆，再準備荷蘭汁，以蛋黃、牛油、檸檬汁及松露醬製成，將巴馬火腿、露荀及溫泉玉子放在酵母包上，最後淋上荷蘭汁即成。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/0zbdUqhC1XSG85p0a9PpWw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290688&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04395&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/J_HzpaGWTHVHdnBTdTW5Eg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290689&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04400&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/mkEeniAv4i5H28CbedeERw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290690&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04416&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;雖然好像很複雜，可是做起來卻簡單得多，可在家自製。未吃已可聞到一股香噴噴的黑松露香，蛋香、火腿油脂香及松露香混為一體，很美味，而且露荀更是鮮嫩可口，平衡了口感，實在是簡單而非常美味。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/7Dtce1BKhIi2WtafS4w5qQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290705&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04479&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;接著便是「溫泉玉子&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Carbonara&lt;/span&gt;」，&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Esther&lt;/span&gt;便由造麵開始教起，先將手造蛋麵的材料混合，慢慢搓成粉團，並讓其靜止&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;分鐘。終於到我們動手了，&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Esther&lt;/span&gt;教曉我們如何使用壓粉團機及切麵機，做成一個又一個麵團來，實在很有趣。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/S8k_QxAGpx9jtvr.qU9zbA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290710&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04448&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/nYk2z8hdN7YygHGNowEgyg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290697&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04451&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;separator&quot; style=&quot;clear: both; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogledrive.com%2Fhost%2F0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k%2FesP1PPz4BOYBSZFs0CjMrg.jpg&amp;amp;container=blogger&amp;amp;gadget=a&amp;amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*&quot; imageanchor=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/esP1PPz4BOYBSZFs0CjMrg.jpg&quot; height=&quot;320&quot; id=&quot;1290699&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04454&quot; width=&quot;240&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogledrive.com%2Fhost%2F0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k%2FjBBYvpKRJUkSS5DIw.zCyw.jpg&amp;amp;container=blogger&amp;amp;gadget=a&amp;amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*&quot; imageanchor=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/jBBYvpKRJUkSS5DIw.zCyw.jpg&quot; height=&quot;320&quot; id=&quot;1290698&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04453&quot; width=&quot;240&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;separator&quot; style=&quot;clear: both; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogledrive.com%2Fhost%2F0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k%2FB45CguMwegjLfoc8EmWdLQ.jpg&amp;amp;container=blogger&amp;amp;gadget=a&amp;amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*&quot; imageanchor=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/B45CguMwegjLfoc8EmWdLQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;320&quot; id=&quot;1290701&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04459&quot; width=&quot;240&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogledrive.com%2Fhost%2F0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k%2F6jqclDQlyX9BRX4EfgmQ8Q.jpg&amp;amp;container=blogger&amp;amp;gadget=a&amp;amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*&quot; imageanchor=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/6jqclDQlyX9BRX4EfgmQ8Q.jpg&quot; height=&quot;320&quot; id=&quot;1290700&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04457&quot; width=&quot;240&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/9TBNqOVRyeAf20eeTUf29A.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290702&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04463&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;麵團煮好後，便去開始煮&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Carbonara&lt;/span&gt;了。輕輕將&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Pancetta&lt;/span&gt;炒過，蛋黃及芝士混合成芝士蛋漿，將意粉及煙肉放入拌勻，再放上一隻溫泉玉子在面，十分美觀。這個吃來美味，可是有點滯，易一邊吃，一邊喝點香檳來平衡一下。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/Gltd5mnHY_citHyZdEf5IA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; id=&quot;1290692&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04428&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/cXXyOJRmHTGpcIKORqlKjA.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290707&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04481&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;除此之外，我們更可品嚐到上述所提過的日韓祭美食，整體味道也不俗，當中的關東煮，我亦十分喜愛，什麼忌廉芝士魚餅、豆腐炸魚球及角切魚餅等等也盡入我口。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/Sv6YhBuVrN4msycMerEk2w.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290706&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04480&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;最後，以一個&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Haagen-Dazs&lt;/span&gt;的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Summer Berries &amp;amp; Cream&lt;/span&gt;威化雪糕三文治作甜品，實在非常滿足。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrap &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://googledrive.com/host/0BwslLG3_gL_yVXFBcHR5N2VDR0k/gyJyiFb7syIs_Mr50S_2wQ.jpg&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; id=&quot;1290708&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 550px;&quot; title=&quot;DSC04485&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #073763; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;這次的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Tasting Event&lt;/span&gt;別出心栽，既可吃到美食，又可學到煮食技巧，一舉兩得，而且&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Esther&lt;/span&gt;的細心教學，又令人明白易懂，將來一定要抽時間跟她學煮多幾項美食才行。另外，這樣簡單易製，必會再到&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Eleven&lt;/span&gt;買些溫泉玉子來造給家人吃。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #073763; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: inherit; font-size: large;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #073763; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;如大家有興趣索取以上食譜，留下Email給我吧！&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #073763; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #073763; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #073763; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #38761d;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Donna Dolce Kitchen Studio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;觀塘駿業里6號富利工業大廈8樓B室&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&